 I ca=\r\nn think of him or the Mother and answer spiritual queries of people confide=\r\nntly and I will end up writing things that would be useful to people. That =\r\nis why I write, as an instrument enabled by my guru. I am not a realized yo=\r\ngi myself. One can view me as a sign on the highway that shows direction to=\r\n Delhi. The sign itself may not have been to Delhi but it may still help so=\r\nme people reach Delhi, if it was installed correctly and not disturbed by t=\r\nhe winds (thoughts of one&#39;s own logical mind and intuitive mind) too much.\n=\r\n&gt;  \n&gt; Best regards,\n&gt; Narasimha\n&gt; -----------------------------------------=\r\n--------------------------\n&gt;   Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons,=\r\n Jyotish Writings,\n&gt; &quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pi=\r\ntri Tarpana:\n&gt;                   http://www.VedicAstrologer.org\n&gt;      Film=\r\ns that make a difference: http://SaraswatiFilms.org \n&gt;      Spirituality: h=\r\nttp://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom\n&gt;   Jyotish writings: http://grou=\r\nps.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings\n&gt; --------------------------------------=\r\n-----------------------------\n&gt;  \n&gt; ---- silentadmirer_in &lt;silentadmirer_in=\r\n@...&gt; wrote:\n&gt; &gt; Namaskar,\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt; &gt; If one is meant to divinize physical f=\r\norm like Mahavatar Babaji has done, divine will will then make one to do so=\r\n.\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt; Divinity (Agni) has been working through nature, to evolve the ph=\r\nysical form from mineral,plant,animal to human. Divine will has already set=\r\n the opportunity right before all the Physically-embodied human beings to t=\r\nake the next step towards perfection of being.\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt; &gt; But, one conscious=\r\nly pursuing it is likely to retain fascination for the physical form, not r=\r\nealize Self and get nowhere.\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt; It was ones&#39; fascination for Physical =\r\nform 